Task 3: Log Retention and Normalization
Step 3.1: Configure Log Rotation
Create logrotate configuration:

sudo nano /etc/logrotate.d/siem-logs
Add configuration:

/var/log/auth.log {
    daily
    rotate 30
    compress
    delaycompress
    missingok
    notifempty
    create 640 syslog adm
}

/var/log/apache2/*.log {
    daily
    rotate 30
    compress
    delaycompress
    missingok
    notifempty
    create 640 root adm
    sharedscripts
    postrotate
        systemctl reload apache2
    endscript
}
Test configuration:

# Dry run
sudo logrotate -d /etc/logrotate.d/siem-logs

# Force rotation for testing
sudo logrotate -f /etc/logrotate.d/siem-logs
